org.testah.driver.http

Class HttpWrapperV2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.testah.driver.http.AbstractHttpWrapper
      • org.testah.driver.http.HttpWrapperV2

  • public class HttpWrapperV2
extends AbstractHttpWrapper
    The type Http wrapper v 2. Sets important timeouts that is not set by default in V1. Also turns off ExpectContinueEnabled which will cause issues if used with Zap proxy
